# Template exclusion configuration
# Files matching these patterns will be excluded when using degit

# Changeset artifacts (version management - not needed in new projects)
.changeset/** export-ignore
**/CHANGELOG.md export-ignore

# Task artifacts
.task/** export-ignore

# Documentation artifacts
docs/PUBLISHING.md export-ignore
CONTRIBUTING.md export-ignore
TEMPLATE_PROPOSAL.md export-ignore

# CI/CD artifacts (let users configure their own)
.github/workflows/publish.yml export-ignore

# Local development artifacts
.env export-ignore
.env.local export-ignore

# Build artifacts
**/node_modules/** export-ignore
**/build/** export-ignore
**/.next/** export-ignore
